│ passed to `ConstantFoldConstant`.                                           │
│                                                                             │
│ My analysis shows that the correct fix is to check for this specific case:  │
│ when `RetVal` is null (void function) but the call type is non-void.        │
│                                                                             │
│ However, the tests are failing because:                                     │
│                                                                             │
│ 1. `evaluate-constfold-call.ll` expects the global to remain uninitialized, │
